name: Ayam Pop - Dotonbori
description:
Ayam Pop is a typical food from Indonesia, West Sumatra, the place where I was born. When I'm in Japan I feel homesick for my hometown. but I'm not sad to be amused by the sparkling lights of the Dotonbori, pachinko and glico.
and... Now I'm confused about whether I miss Sumatra or Japan?
